rComments: BEST PROF EVER! He is so clear, doesn't make things difficult, articulates concepts really well and clearly! Cannot endorse him as a prof more! In 1L you don't get to choose, but if you did, pick this guy all the way! AMAZING!!! Made tort law a breeze, and the easiest class just because of his teaching alone!!
Chapman is very clear and makes every case fun and interesting. I wish more professors were like him.

Chapman is the kind of prof you want to sit with for an entire weekend and have him just talk at you. Everything he says is eloquent, thoughtful, and fascinating. Wasn't all that interested in the course to begin with, but he blew me away. I agree-- best prof. ever.
Amazing professor.  Makes the material always engaging.  Helpful, insightful, there are no limits to his knowledge of his field of law.  Best professor ever, anywhere.
very bright and very thoughtful, a genuinely nice guy
Chapman is a very clear and organized speaker. He makes issues really easy to understand.
Great prof to have at 9 a.m.!  Has a sense of humour and fields questions very well.
Very organized and thorough approach.  Responds well to questions.  Helps explain other concepts and ties the material together very well.
